Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:15.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}痛彻心扉的是无辜的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:20.33,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}信じたいよ 孤独じゃないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:20.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}我相信自己并不孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:25.70,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}此処は彷徨いのParadise
