Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:38.38,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}もし君の瞳に 辿り着けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:38.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}若能映入你的眼眸
